content.text: Hi, we are still looking for our pastries and drinks packaging. What is the best time to call you? I prefer zoom call if that's ok

content.thinking: Handoff to human team for a call.

content.text:
Great to hear you're moving forward with packaging for pastries and drinks!

Absolutely, we do Zoom calls. Let me connect you with our sourcing team to set one up. Could you share your email and preferred time/timezone? I'll have someone reach out to schedule.

In the meantime — are you looking at boxes, pouches, cups, or a mix? A quick idea of the packaging style helps our team prep relevant options and pricing before the call.
jammaica.devera@gmail.com. Im available tomorrow 2:30 or 3pm Philippine time. We need boxes for pastries and cups for drinks, maybe 5000 units each

Perfect, thanks! I'll pass this along to our team:

- *Email:* jammaica.devera@gmail.com
- *Zoom call:* Tomorrow, 2:30 or 3:00 PM Philippine time
- *Products:* Pastry boxes + drink cups
- *Quantity:* ~5,000 units each

For pastry boxes, typical range is $0.15–0.50/unit depending on material (kraft, cardboard, window cutout) and print. Cups run $0.03–0.15/unit depending on size and custom branding.

Someone from our team will reach out to confirm the call time. Do you have any reference photos or styles in mind? That'll help them come prepared with the right options.
